On how the AI industry's framing shapes the research and policy agenda. Reinforces the chapter's "trapped scientists" argument.
Bender, E. M., & Hanna, A. (2025). The AI Con: How to fight Big Tech's hype and create the future we want. Harper.
A direct critique of AI industry rhetoric. Aligned with the chapter's argument that mystifying language serves commercial interests.
